snippet.title: Chivalry 2 - Weapons of War Teasers (Compilation Part 1)
snippet.description:
A compilation of recent weapon teaser videos that we've shared on our Chivalry 2 social channels throughout 2020. Sign up for alpha: https://chivalry2.com/alpha

Stay tuned for more teasers, and read our End of 2020 Development Update: https://chivalry2.com/2020/12/18/end-of-2020/
